    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows its age. The engine runs consistently and the car is fully operational, but you should expect some cosmetic wear on the interior and minor scratches on the exterior. Mechanically, it is sound for now, though it may require some routine maintenance or minor part replacements in the near future to keep it in peak shape. It\u2019s a solid, functional choice for someone looking for a dependable vehicle at a more accessible price point.",
