    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, which exemplifies both mechanical integrity and aesthetic appeal. Having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection, this specimen offers a refined driving experience and a sophisticated presence. It represents an ideal acquisition for the professional seeking a reliable, high-caliber vehicle that balances performance with long-term value. We invite serious inquiries to appreciate the superior condition of this offering.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
