      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s looking for a brand-new home! This car has been super well-loved and is still running like a total dream. It\u2019s in really great shape and is absolutely perfect for everything from your daily commute to those fun weekend road trips. You\u2019re going to love how smooth it feels on the road! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 997-generation Carrera delivers a visceral, analog driving experience. Powered by a mid-mounted 3.6L flat-six, the powerplant exhibits excellent linear power delivery and high-revving stability. The 6-speed manual gearbox offers precise gate engagement, paired with a rear-wheel-drive chassis optimized for neutral handling. Equipped with Porsche Active Suspension Management (PASM) and a multi-link rear suspension, the car maintains exceptional mechanical grip and composure through technical corners. Recent maintenance includes a comprehensive inspection of the IMS bearing and a new set of high-performance tires. While it displays honest signs of use, the drivetrain remains tight and responsive, offering a superb balance of performance and value.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Engine runs smooth. Interior is clean. All maintenance up to date. Ready for immediate use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a remarkable example of reliability and refined performance. The exterior paint retains a deep, glossy finish, though close inspection reveals minor stone chips on the hood consistent with careful highway driving. The body panels are straight, with no major dings or scratches. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean and smoke-free; the premium leather upholstery shows light, natural creasing but remains free of any tears or stains. All electronic components, from the responsive infotainment system to the dual-zone climate control, function perfectly. Mechanically, this car has been fastidiously maintained, with a full service history documenting regular oil changes and a recent comprehensive brake service. The engine delivers smooth, consistent power, and the transmission shifts flawlessly. It sits on a set of high-quality tires with plenty of tread remaining. This is a solid, turn-key vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably maintained vehicle, which serves as a testament to disciplined ownership and rigorous mechanical upkeep. This specimen offers a refined driving experience, characterized by its robust performance and an interior that retains a high degree of its original sophistication. Every component has been scrutinized to ensure it meets our exacting standards for reliability and presentation. This is an exceptional opportunity for the professional seeking a premium automotive asset that balances distinguished character with substantial functional value.",
      "price": 36800.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and it's been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for me. Whether you're commuting or heading out on a weekend road trip, this car handles beautifully and feels great on the road. It's clean, well-cared for, and totally ready for its next adventure! I'm sad to see it go, but I know it'll make the next owner very happy. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 10
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This 2008 Porsche Cayman S is a masterclass in mid-engine dynamics, powered by a 3.4L flat-six engine featuring VarioCam Plus for an optimized power band. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp 6-speed manual transaxle, ensuring direct mechanical connection and precise heel-toe downshifts. The chassis features a MacPherson strut suspension geometry that has been meticulously maintained, with recent bushing inspections to ensure lateral stiffness remains within factory tolerances. Performance is augmented by four-piston monobloc aluminum fixed calipers and cross-drilled, internally vented rotors, providing exceptional heat dissipation and firm pedal feel. The interior and exterior show honest road-going patina, but the mechanical vitals\u2014including cooling system pressure tests and oil analysis\u2014confirm a robust, high-revving powerplant ready for the apex. This is a purist's specification, prioritized for kinematic excellence and tactile feedback.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
